---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="privacy - leshy" description="how this site handles your data" bodyClass="post-page">

  <nav class="post-nav">
    <a href="/">&larr; home</a>
  </nav>

  <header class="post-header">
    <h1>privacy</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>this site is run by leshy. here's what happens with your data.</p>

    <h2>analytics</h2>
    <p>this site uses <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">cloudflare web analytics</a> to understand how many people visit and which pages they read. it does not use cookies, does not track you across sites, and does not collect personal information. no data is sold or shared with advertisers.</p>

    <h2>email list</h2>
    <p>if you subscribe to the mailing list, your email address is stored by <a href="https://mailchimp.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">mailchimp</a>, which processes it on our behalf. your email is used only to send occasional updates about new music and writings. it is never sold or shared with third parties.</p>
    <p>every email includes an unsubscribe link. you can also contact me directly to have your email removed.</p>

    <h2>third-party embeds</h2>
    <p>some pages may include embedded content from spotify. these embeds are loaded directly from spotify's servers and are subject to <a href="https://www.spotify.com/legal/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">spotify's privacy policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>external links</h2>
    <p>this site links to platforms like bandcamp, youtube, instagram, tiktok, and x. clicking those links takes you to sites with their own privacy policies that are outside of our control.</p>

    <h2>contact</h2>
    <p>if you have questions about how your data is handled, reach out on any of the platforms linked on the <a href="/">home page</a>.</p>

    <hr />

    <p><em>last updated: april 2026</em></p>
  </div>

</Base>
